You must have your own cable to charge!

When you arrive at the location, insert the cable into charger and into the car, click "Start charging" in the app. More detailed information - in the "About our service" section of the GO TO-U app. More GO TO-U charging stations are displayed exclusively in the mobile application. The charging stations are universal.

You must have your own cable to charge!  Support - 0 800 217 007

When you arrive at the location, insert the cable into charger and into the car, click "Start charging" in the app. More detailed information - in the "About our service" section of the GO TO-U app. More GO TO-U charging stations are displayed exclusively in the mobile application. You must have your own cable to charge! The charging stations are universal!  Support - 0 800 217 007

GeneralComments: Раді Вас бачити на зарядній станції IONITY, що на сьогоднішній день є найбільшим інвестиційним проектом в частині розміщення і управління мережею зарядних станцій для електромобілів в Україні.  Для можливості підключення Вашого електромобіля до зарядної станції, будь-ласка, завантажте мобільний додаток EcoFactor за наступними посиланнями:  для користувачів iOS: https://apps.apple.com/us/app/ecofactor-network/id1438716797?ls=1  для користувачів Android: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=eu.ecofactor&hl=en  Після реєстрації у додатку для Вас будуть доступні наступні функції: - старт/стоп зарядної станції; - перегляд статусу зарядної станції (зайнята/вільна); - перегляду та поповнення Вашого балансу; - перегляду процесу заряду Вашого електромобіля та кількість спожитої електроенергії, а також багато інших зручних функцій.  Цілодобова підтримка за номером - 095 200 7 002  Для отримання більше інформації про нашу мережу, будь-ласка, відвідайте наш сайт https://www.ionity.ua _________________________  Good to see you at the IONITY Charging Station. To date, IONITY is the largest charging stations deployment and management investment project in Ukraine.  To connect your EV to a charging station, please download the EcoFactor mobile App with the following links:  for iOS users: https://apps.apple.com/us/app/ecofactor-network/id1438716797?ls=1  for Android users: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=eu.ecofactor&hl=en  After registering in the App you will have the following features available: - Start / stop of the charging station; - View charging station status (busy / free); - Reviewing and replenishing your balance; - View the charging process of your EV and the amount of electricity consumed, as well as many other convenient features.  For 24/7 support - 095 200 7 002

You must have your own cable to charge!  Support - 0 800 217 007

GeneralComments: To charge, you need to install the "GO TO-U" mobile application  iOS: https://apps.apple.com/ua/app/to-u/id1175538017 Android: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.go.tou  Then, select a charging station on the map and reserve it for the required time. When you arrive at the location, insert the cable into charger and into the car, click "Start charging" in the app. More detailed information - in the "About our service" section of the GO TO-U app. More GO TO-U charging stations are displayed exclusively in the mobile application. The charging stations are universal.

GeneralComments:
[ENG below]
Зарядна станція потужністю 60 кВт, доступна 24/7.
Для того, щоб зарядитись, Вам необхідно встановити мобільний додаток «TO-U».

iOS: https://apps.apple.com/ua/app/to-u/id1175538017
Android: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.go.tou

Оберіть на карті додатку необхідну зарядну станцію та встановіть або забронюйте наперед необхідний час заряджання. Після прибуття до станції, вставте кабель в зарядку та в авто, натисніть в додатку «Розпочати заряджання».

Час між вставленням кабелю та початком сесії (таймаут) не повинен перевищувати 400 секунд.
Детальніша інструкція знаходиться у розділі «Про сервіс» мобільного додатку TO-U.

Для заряджання через Type 2 необхідно мати власний кабель.

Зверніть увагу, вночі ворота комплексу зачиняються в цілях безпеки, проте станція доступна та працює, немає жодних обмежень щодо заряджання, номер телефону, щоб відчинити ворота вночі: +380968840854

Більше зарядних станцій платформи GO TO-U відображені виключно в мобільному додатку.

[English]
60 kWh charging station, available 24/7.
To charge, you need to install the "TO-U" mobile application.

iOS: https://apps.apple.com/ua/app/to-u/id1175538017
Android: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.go.tou

To charge the car, select a charging station on the map and setup or book the required charging time. When you arrive at the location, insert the cable into charger and into the car, click "Start charging" in the app.

You have 400 seconds timeout to initiate/start the charging session.
More detailed information - is in the "About our service" section of the TO-U app.

It would help to have your cable to charge the car with a Type 2 charger.

The station is available 24/7. Please note - the gates of the Hotel are closed at night for security purposes, but the station is available and working, there are no charging restrictions, and here is the phone number to open the gates at night: +380968840854

More TO-U charging stations are available exclusively in the TO-U mobile app.

GeneralComments:
Registration, top-up & charging via 'STRUM Charging' mobile app (iOS/Android), at least 25.00 kWh must be available on the account at the start of each charging session. Parking is free. You can book your STRUM card only after registrartion & top-up by sending request to support.strum@dtek.com.
 
 You pay only for kWh, no fees for time or session. Price during top-up is 9 UAH/KWH (≈ 0.3 €/KWH). While charging on CHAdeMO/CCS, 1 KWH is taken away for each 1 kWh of charging. While charging on Type2, 0.5 KWH is taken away for each 1 kWh of charging (half price). Actual prices at http://strum.dtek.com/en/prices/.
 
 Android App download - https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.beenergised.chargemobile.dtek&hl=en
 iOS App download - https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/strum-charging/id1368596475?mt=8

GeneralComments:
Registration, top-up & charging via 'STRUM Charging' mobile app (iOS/Android), at least 25.00 kWh must be available on the account at the start of each charging session. Parking is free. You can book your STRUM card only after registrartion & top-up by sending request to support.strum@dtek.com.

GeneralComments:
Registration, top-up & charging via 'STRUM Charging' mobile app (iOS/Android), at least 25.00 kWh must be available on the account at the start of each charging session. You can book your STRUM card only after registrartion & top-up by sending request to support.strum@dtek.com. 

    You pay only for kWh, no fees for time or session. Price during top up is 9 UAH/KWH (≈ 0.3 €/KWH). While charging on CHAdeMO/CCS, 1 KWH is taken away for each 1 kWh of charging. While charging on Type2, 0.5 KWH is taken away for each 1 kWh of charging (half price). Actual prices at http://strum.dtek.com/en/prices/. 

    Android App download - https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.beenergised.chargemobile.dtek&hl=en
    iOS App download - https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/strum-charging/id1368596475?mt=8

AddressInfo.AccessComments: Access Sunday-Thursday 10:00-22:00, Friday-Saturday 10:00-23:00. Entrance from B.Khmelnitsky Street. Floor P1 of underground parking (minus first floor), parking lots № 39-40, 57-58. The first 14 of parking minutes are free, then 50 UAH/h. If you do not pick up the car at night - a fine of 100 UAH/h. STRUM card doesn't enable free parking at this location.

GeneralComments:
Registration, top-up & charging via 'STRUM Charging' mobile app (iOS/Android), at least 25.00 kWh must be available on the account at the start of each charging session. Parking is free. You can book your STRUM card only after registrartion & top-up by sending request to support.strum@dtek.com.

You pay only for kWh, no fees for time or session. Price during top-up is 9 UAH/KWH (≈ 0.3 €/KWH). While charging on CHAdeMO/CCS, 1 KWH is taken away for each 1 kWh of charging. While charging on Type2, 0.5 KWH is taken away for each 1 kWh of charging (half price). Actual prices at http://strum.dtek.com/en/prices/.

Android App download - https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.beenergised.chargemobile.dtek&hl=en
iOS App download - https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/strum-charging/id1368596475?mt=8

AddressInfo.AccessComments: 24h access. Entrance from Velika Okruzhna Street or Glushkov Avenue. Open parking lot on the east side of the mall. STRUM card doesn't enable free parking at this location.

GeneralComments:
Registration, top-up & charging via 'STRUM Charging' mobile app (iOS/Android), at least 25.00 kWh must be available on the account at the start of each charging session. Additional cost of parking - from 07:00 to 23:00 is 20 UAH / 30 minutes, at night from 23:00 to 07:00 is 16 UAH / 30 minutes, leaving in first 14 minutes is free. Parking is free for 1 hour with STRUM card. You can book your STRUM card only after registrartion & top-up by sending request to support.strum@dtek.com.

You pay only for kWh, no fees for time or session. Price during top-up is 9 UAH/KWH (≈ 0.3 €/KWH). While charging on CHAdeMO/CCS, 1 KWH is taken away for each 1 kWh of charging. While charging on Type2, 0.5 KWH is taken away for each 1 kWh of charging (half price). Actual prices at http://strum.dtek.com/en/prices/.

Registration, top-up & charging via 'STRUM Charging' mobile app (iOS/Android), at least 25.00 kWh must be available on the account at the start of each charging session. Parking is free. You can book your STRUM card only after registrartion & top-up by sending request to support.strum@dtek.com.

You pay only for kWh, no fees for time or session. Price during top up is 9 UAH/KWH (≈ 0.3 €/KWH). While charging on CHAdeMO/CCS, 1 KWH is taken away for each 1 kWh of charging. While charging on Type2, 0.5 KWH is taken away for each 1 kWh of charging (half price). Actual prices at http://strum.dtek.com/en/prices/.

Android App download - https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.beenergised.chargemobile.dtek&hl=en
iOS App download - https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/strum-charging/id1368596475?mt=8

AddressInfo.AccessComments: На 5 (ПЯТОМ) уровне ОТДЕЛЬНО СТОЯЩЕГО паркинга есть несколько стандартных розеток 16А. Просьба заряжаться по тихому, не привлекая внимание персонала. Ещё раз. Работают НЕ ВСЕ РОЗЕТКИ. Зарядиться можно НА ПЯТОМ уровне ОТДЕЛЬНО СТОЯЩЕГО (ВНЕШНЕГО) паркинга. Чем меньше мы привлекаем внимание персонала, тем дольше проживёт месторождение электронов. Для тех кто в танке повторяю: слоняться по парковке и докапываться до персонала где можно зарядиться (а так же дать кабель и так далее) НЕ НАДО.
